dmca.title: Author Regrets "Psychological Profile" Story
dmca.body:
1: The copyrighted work is titled:

PSYCHOLOGICAL PROFILE OF THE TROUBLED FEMALE TEEN 
Author - [private]
Date - 5/25/98

I am the author of this and I distributed it freely. However, I have come to realize that it is something that I do not want to be available as it is a very negative piece of writing. This is not causing me any monetary harm, I simply do not want my writing to be publicly available anymore. I have contacted many of the other websites who have hosted this piece and I may send another request for removal if I am unable to contact the site owners and have them blank out the document so that it will not be re-cached.

2:  Google groups search query: "troubled female teen"
